channel.title: Can't get anything right
channel.description: O.K. I've been working on going for a server for a long time. I've tried every tutoriial and always get so close to making a server work but I just can't get it to fully work. I am looking for a good and easy 317 server with pickup and to be able to have a webclient with it. If someone could Teamview me and help, I would be willing to pay up to $30 for the work done. Please respond or message if you are able to help. Thanks for reading, Tyler

item.title: Can't get anything right
item.dc:creator: @_N_eon (N)eon
item.description:
@_N_eon wrote:

Do this:
Search bar- hybrid Pvp

Download the source and the client ( not webclient )
Extract both to your desktop.
Make a new folder on desktop and drop the client and source you extracted into the new folder.
From their just change the Ip’s, compile it ( but first you need to edit the compiling to your java ) Then run it. You can edit the shops and everything else… Just follow those tutorials…

Hope I helped…

If you need anything comment back.
